snippet.title: NES Longplay [128] Chip 'n Dale: Rescue Rangers (2P)
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by:  Tsunao & Genbu

Platformer by friggin' Capcom.

Something about a kitteh missing and Ch-ch-ch-Chip 'n Dale (Rescue Rangers) set out on an adventure.  A fat cat is involved.

I control Chip (Player 1) while bro controls Dale (Player 2).  Skills may or may not be involved.  Game is harder in two players.  I don't think my bro played this game.  He also blames the controller (and I am using an inferior controller.)  Deaths here and there (mainly bro.  I wouldn't die a lot if I played solo.)

I love this game's music.  My picks:  boss music, Zone B, Zone J, the main theme.

-floating 1-Up Star appears-
Me:  "Stop stealing my stars." -
Disclaimer: Most videos by World of Longplays use SaveStates!
